Invocation Name: blockbuster quiz
des:
Blockbuster Quiz is the fun movies, cinema and video quiz for anyone who remembers the Seventies, Eighties or Nineties!

Can you remember who directed Independence Day, exactly who E.T. wanted to phone... or even why Logan was Running?

Relive your youth, maybe remember some great movies, popcorn tinted trips to the cinema and even some long forgotten B movies you rented on VHS!

Play on your own or with friends - who can get the highest score?
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
